'''拉克什亚·森'''（{{lang-en|Lakshya Sen}}，{{bd|2001年|8月16日}}），[[印度|印度]]男子[[羽毛球|羽毛球]]運動員。

== 生涯 ==
=== 早年 ===
拉克什亞·森出生於[[印度|印度]]的[[阿尔莫拉|阿尔莫拉]][[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]，他的父親是一位羽毛球教練而他的兄長[[Chirag_Sen|奇拉格·森]]同為羽毛球運動員<ref name="Born place"/>。

=== 青年時期 ===
拉克什亞·森在青年時期便表現亮眼，在2014年時年僅13歲的他便在瑞士青年錦標賽斬獲冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/18635905/badminton-sourabh-varma-beats-lakshya-sen-win-national-championship-final|title='Disciplined' Lakshya Sen tipped for great success|work=ESPN|date=2017-02-07|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610025522/https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/18635905/badminton-sourabh-varma-beats-lakshya-sen-win-national-championship-final|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後2015年，他在印度青年錦標賽以2比0（21比18、21比15）戰勝他的哥哥獲得冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.india.com/sports/ruthvika-shivani-gadde-lakshya-sen-win-junior-international-badminton-championship-538734/|title=Ruthvika Shivani Gadde, Lakshya Sen win Junior International Badminton Championship|work=India.com|date=2015-09-07|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2015-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030194655/http://www.india.com/sports/ruthvika-shivani-gadde-lakshya-sen-win-junior-international-badminton-championship-538734/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年7月，拉克什亞·森代表印度参加[[泰國|泰國]][[曼谷|曼谷]]举办的[[2016年亞洲青年羽毛球錦標賽|亞洲青年羽毛球錦標賽]]，他從首圈一路殺進準決賽並以0比2不敵來自[[中國|中國]]的[[孫飛翔|孫飛翔]]，獲得季軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-bronze-medal-asian-junior-badminton-championships|title=Lakshya Sen wins the bronze medal at the Asian Junior Badminton Championships|work=sportskeeda|date=2016-07-18|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2016-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112073735/http://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-bronze-medal-asian-junior-badminton-championships|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月，他首次出戰成年國際賽事、[[2016年印度羽毛球國際系列賽|印度國際系列賽]]男子單打項目，在決賽中以3比1的成績（11-13、11-3、11-6、11-6）擊敗了馬來西亞新秀[[李梓嘉|李梓嘉]]，奪得個人生涯中首個國際賽冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/shuttler-lakshya-sen-clinches-gold-in-senior-india-international-series/articleshow/55650452.cms|title=Shuttler Lakshya Sen clinches gold in Senior India International Series|work=The Times of India|date=2016-11-27|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413200042/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/shuttler-lakshya-sen-clinches-gold-in-senior-india-international-series/articleshow/55650452.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後在2017年，拉克什亞·森陸續收穫[[2017年保加利亞羽毛球公開賽|保加利亞公開賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-bulgaria-open-international-series/articleshow/60102782.cms|title=Lakshya Sen wins Bulgaria Open International Series|work=The Times of India|date=2017-08-17|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610034125/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-bulgaria-open-international-series/articleshow/60102782.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[2017年印度羽毛球國際系列賽|印度國際系列賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://scroll.in/field/859317/badminton-lakshya-sen-m-tanishq-win-india-international-singles-titles|title=Badminton: Lakshya Sen, M Tanishq win India International singles titles|work=Scroll.in|date=2017-11-26|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610033006/https://scroll.in/field/859317/badminton-lakshya-sen-m-tanishq-win-india-international-singles-titles|dead-url=no}}</ref>的冠軍和[[2017年印度羽毛球國際挑戰賽|印度國際挑戰賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-stunned-by-thai-shuttler-thammasin-in-final/articleshow/61905388.cms|title=Lakshya Sen stunned by Thai shuttler Thammasin in final|work=The Times of India|date=2017-12-03|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610033411/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-stunned-by-thai-shuttler-thammasin-in-final/articleshow/61905388.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>的亞軍。拉克什亞·森更是在2017年登上了世界羽聯青年世界排名的第一位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/en/news/lakshya-sen-badminton-achievements|title=Lakshya Sen, the new poster boy of Indian badminton|work=Olympics|date=2022-05-26|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609001013/https://olympics.com/en/news/lakshya-sen-badminton-achievements|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年7月，拉克什亞·森代表印度兼六號種子参加[[印尼|印尼]][[雅加达|雅加达]]举办的[[2018年亞洲青年羽毛球錦標賽|亞洲青年羽毛球錦標賽]]，他從首圈一路闖進決賽並面對賽會頭號種子、世青賽冠軍[[昆拉武特·威提讪|昆拉武特·威提讪]]以直落兩局挑落對手奪下冠軍，亦是印度羽壇史上第一位亞青賽男單冠軍得主<ref>{{zh-cn}}{{cite news|title=羽球亚青赛国羽锁定两金 女单会师男单无缘决赛|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/others/badmin/2018-07-22/doc-ihfqtahi7607601.shtml|agency=新浪体育|date=2018-07-22|accessdate=2018-10-12|archive-date=2018-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012094420/http://sports.sina.com.cn/others/badmin/2018-07-22/doc-ihfqtahi7607601.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年10月，他代表印度参加[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[布宜諾斯艾利斯|布宜諾斯艾利斯]]舉辦的[[2018年夏季青年奧林匹克運動會羽球比賽|2018年青年奧運會羽球比賽]]。男單决赛中，他以0比2（15-21、19-21）不敵中國選手[[李诗沣|李诗沣]]，獲得男單銀牌<ref>{{zh-cn}}{{Cite news|url=http://sports.qq.com/a/20181013/002340.htm|title=青奥会羽球李诗沣男单夺冠 王祉怡负吴堇溦摘银|date=2018-10-13|work=腾讯体育|accessdate=2018-10-14|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013053819/http://sports.qq.com/a/20181013/002340.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並在隨後進行的混合團體決賽中幫助隊伍獲得金牌。隨後一個月，他代表印度参加[[加拿大|加拿大]][[萬錦市|萬錦市]]举办的[[2018年世界青年羽毛球錦標賽|世界青年羽毛球錦標賽]]，在男單準决赛以1比2（22-20、16-21、13-21）不敌衛冕冠軍、泰國的[[昆拉武特·威提讪|昆拉武特·威提讪]]，拿下季軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-bronze-medal-world-juniors-5452025/|title=Lakshya Sen goes down in semis of World Junior Championship, wins bronze medal|work=The Indian Express|date=2018-11-18|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806021326/https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-bronze-medal-world-juniors-5452025/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後他再出戰[[2018年印度羽毛球國際挑戰賽|印度國際挑戰賽]]，並在決賽中再次對壘[[昆拉武特·威提讪|昆拉武特·威提讪]]，這次他以2比0擊敗對手贏得冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshay-sen-wins-gold-at-tata-open-india-international-challenge|title=Lakshya Sen wins gold at Tata Open India International Challenge|work=sportskeeda|date=2018-12-02|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220110829/https://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshay-sen-wins-gold-at-tata-open-india-international-challenge|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2019年－2020年 ===
2019年起，拉克什亞·森開始參加較高級別的[[2019年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽|世界羽聯世界巡迴賽]]賽事，他在3月時出戰100級別的[[2019年中國陵水羽毛球大師賽|中國陵水大師賽]]，但最後他不敵東道主的[[翁泓陽|翁泓陽]]栽在準決賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-china-masters-semifinal-report/article26556394.ece|title=China Masters: Lakshya Sen crashes out in semifinals|work=Sportstar|date=2019-03-16|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506131123/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-china-masters-semifinal-report/article26556394.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後他轉戰歐洲賽事，他先是在[[2019年波蘭羽毛球公開賽|波蘭公開賽]]拿下亞軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ppba.in/lakshya-settles-for-silver-in-poland.html|title=Lakshya settles for silver in poland|work=PPBA|date=2019-04-01|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610084725/https://www.ppba.in/lakshya-settles-for-silver-in-poland.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，拉克什亞·森先後奪下[[2019年比利時羽毛球國際賽|比利時國際賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-beats-victor-svendsen-belgium-international-badminton/article29418811.ece|title=Lakshya Sen wins Belgium International Badminton title|work=Sportstar|date=2019-09-14|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413200043/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-beats-victor-svendsen-belgium-international-badminton/article29418811.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[2019年荷蘭羽毛球公開賽|荷蘭公開賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-dutch-open-for-maiden-bwf-world-tour-title/articleshow/71566542.cms|title=Lakshya Sen wins Dutch Open for maiden BWF World Tour title|work=The Times of India|date=2019-10-13|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222115200/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-wins-dutch-open-for-maiden-bwf-world-tour-title/articleshow/71566542.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[2019年薩洛盧羽毛球公開賽|薩洛盧公開賽]]<ref name="Top50">{{cite web|url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-becomes-the-youngest-indian-men-s-singles-shuttler-to-break-into-top-50|title=Lakshya Sen becomes the youngest Indian men's singles shuttler to break into top 50|work=sportskeeda|date=2019-11-05|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610085615/https://www.sportskeeda.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-becomes-the-youngest-indian-men-s-singles-shuttler-to-break-into-top-50|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[2019年蘇格蘭羽毛球公開賽|蘇格蘭羽毛球公開賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/badminton-lakshya-sen-wins-scottish-open-claims-fourth-title-of-the-season-pullela-gopichand/article30074036.ece#:~:text=Fast%2Drising%20Indian%20shuttler%20Lakshya,minute%20final%20on%20Sunday%20night.|title=Lakshya Sen wins Scottish Open, claims fourth title of the season|work=Sportstar|date=2019-11-25|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610085727/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/badminton-lakshya-sen-wins-scottish-open-claims-fourth-title-of-the-season-pullela-gopichand/article30074036.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[2019年孟加拉羽毛球國際挑戰賽|孟加拉國際挑戰賽]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-claims-bangladesh-international-challenge-title-6168720/|title=Lakshya Sen claims Bangladesh International Challenge title|work=The Indian Express|date=2019-12-15|accessdate=2022-06-10|archivedate=2022-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404202702/https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-claims-bangladesh-international-challenge-title-6168720/|dead-url=no}}</ref>五項賽事的冠軍。他的[[世界羽聯世界排名|世界羽聯世界排名]]也隨著這五座冠軍在2019年達到了前50名<ref name="Top50"/>。

2020年2月，拉克什亞·森跟隨[[印度國家羽毛球隊|印度國家羽毛球隊]]一同參加在[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]]舉行的[[2020年亞洲羽毛球團體錦標賽男子團體比賽|亞洲團體錦標賽]]，最終印度在準決賽中以2比3不敵[[印尼國家羽毛球隊|印尼]]，獲得季軍追平了在[[2016年亞洲羽毛球團體錦標賽男子團體比賽|2016年]]的成績<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/india-bronze-medal-indonesia-semifinal-badminton-asia-team-championships-lakshya-sen-jonatan-christie-sai-praneeth-anthony-ginting-chirag-shetty/article30829572.ece|title=India settles for bronze at Badminton Asia Team Championships after loss to Indonesia in semis|work=Sportstar|date=2020-02-15|accessdate=2022-06-14|archivedate=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524162715/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/india-bronze-medal-indonesia-semifinal-badminton-asia-team-championships-lakshya-sen-jonatan-christie-sai-praneeth-anthony-ginting-chirag-shetty/article30829572.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後在3月，拉克什亞·森首次參加[[2020年全英羽毛球公開賽|全英公開賽]]，他先是在首圈以1比2逆轉[[香港|香港]]的[[李卓耀|李卓耀]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/all-england-open-2020-lakshya-sen-pulls-off-a-brilliant-come-from-behind-win-6310183/|title=All England Open 2020: Lakshya Sen pulls off a brilliant come-from-behind win on debut|work=The Indian Express|date=2020-03-12|accessdate=2022-06-14|archivedate=2021-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210619201511/https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/all-england-open-2020-lakshya-sen-pulls-off-a-brilliant-come-from-behind-win-6310183/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後他在次圈面對的是賽會二號種子、[[丹麥|丹麥]]的[[安賽龍|安賽龍]]，雙方激戰45分鐘，最後以拉克什亞·森直落兩局落敗而告終<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/lakshya-sen-all-england-open-2020-campaign-ends-viktor-axelsen-loss-2nd-round-1654937-2020-03-12|title=All England Open: Lakshya Sen's impressive debut campaign ends with loss to Viktor Axelsen|work=India Today|date=2020-03-12|accessdate=2022-06-14|archivedate=2020-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313155625/https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/lakshya-sen-all-england-open-2020-campaign-ends-viktor-axelsen-loss-2nd-round-1654937-2020-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病]]肆虐導致眾多比賽取消，讓拉克什亞·森在這之後便在2020年再無參加任何比賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.enanyang.my/%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BE%BD%E8%81%94%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D-4%E6%9C%8812%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E8%B5%9B%E4%BA%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%81%9C%E6%91%86|title=世界羽联:疫情影响4月12日前赛事全停摆|work=南洋商報|date=2020-03-14|accessdate=2022-03-18|archivedate=2022-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318020753/https://www.enanyang.my/%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BE%BD%E8%81%94%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D-4%E6%9C%8812%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E8%B5%9B%E4%BA%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%81%9C%E6%91%86|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2021年－2022年 ===
2021年3月，拉克什亞·森在2021年的首場比賽是[[2021年瑞士羽毛球公開賽|瑞士公開賽]]，但他在首圈便以0比2不敵[[丹麥|丹麥]]的[[維克多·斯文森|維克多·斯文森]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/swiss-open-sindhu-srikanth-advance-lakshya-prannoy-lose/articleshow/81317004.cms|title=Swiss Open: Sindhu, Srikanth advance; Lakshya, Prannoy lose|work=The Times of India|date=2021-03-03|accessdate=2022-06-15|archivedate=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304014456/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/swiss-open-sindhu-srikanth-advance-lakshya-prannoy-lose/articleshow/81317004.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，拉克什亞出戰[[2021年全英羽毛球公開賽|全英公開賽]]，他在八強賽上以1比2敗給[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]的[[馬克·卡爾尤|馬克·卡爾尤]]，首兩場國際賽事都未能達到準決賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/sports/all-england-open-2021-mark-caljouw-beats-lakshya-sen-in-quarter-finals-ashwini-ponnappa-n-sikki-reddy-bow-out-9440061.html|title=All England Open 2021: Mark Caljouw beats Lakshya Sen in quarter-finals; Ashwini Ponnappa-N Sikki Reddy bow out|work=Firstpost|date=2021-03-19|accessdate=2022-06-15|archivedate=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319162912/https://www.firstpost.com/sports/all-england-open-2021-mark-caljouw-beats-lakshya-sen-in-quarter-finals-ashwini-ponnappa-n-sikki-reddy-bow-out-9440061.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到2021年8月，拉克什亞·森以頭號種子的身份出戰較低級別的[[2021年丹麥羽毛球大師賽|丹麥羽毛球大師賽]]，他在準決賽中對壘賽會三號種子、[[加拿大|加拿大]]的[[楊燦_(羽毛球運動員)|楊燦]]，他先盛後衰以1比2（21比13、14比21、18比21）遭到對手逆轉，止步於四強<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/dehradun/shuttler-lakshya-sen-wins-bronze-at-victor-denmark-masters-2021/articleshow/85159569.cms|title=Shuttler Lakshya Sen wins bronze at Victor Denmark Masters 2021|work=The Times of India|date=2021-08-09|accessdate=2022-06-15|archivedate=2021-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211207091428/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/dehradun/shuttler-lakshya-sen-wins-bronze-at-victor-denmark-masters-2021/articleshow/85159569.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後在同年10月，拉克什亞以頭號種子出戰[[2021年荷蘭羽毛球公開賽|荷蘭公開賽]]，他在決賽中對壘的是新加坡的[[駱建佑|駱建佑]]，他遭到對手直落兩局結束比賽，無緣衛冕冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/en/news/ndian-badminton-dutch-open-2021-results-lakshya-sen-results|title=Dutch Open badminton: Lakshya Sen loses in men’s singles final|work=Olympics|date=2021-10-17|accessdate=2022-06-17|archivedate=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413200037/https://olympics.com/en/news/ndian-badminton-dutch-open-2021-results-lakshya-sen-results|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後他轉戰在歐洲區的[[2021年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽|超級系列賽事]]，但他的成績並不理想，在[[2021年丹麥羽毛球公開賽|丹麥公開賽]]和[[2021年法國羽毛球公開賽|法國公開賽]]分別止步於次圈以及八強賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32449074/lakshya-sen-falters-denmark-open-indian-badminton-olympic-hope-axelsen|title=Lakshya Sen comes apart in Denmark yet remains Indian badminton's brightest hope|work=ESPN|date=2021-10-22|accessdate=2022-06-17|archivedate=2022-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606164311/https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32449074/lakshya-sen-falters-denmark-open-indian-badminton-olympic-hope-axelsen|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aninews.in/news/sports/others/french-open-lakshya-sen-loses-to-heo-kwanghee-in-quarter-finals20211029191958/#:~:text=French%20Open%3A%20Lakshya%20Sen%20loses%20to%20Heo%20Kwanghee%20in%20quarter%2Dfinals,-ANI%20%7C%20Updated%3A%20Oct&text=Paris%20%5BFrance%5D%2C%20October%2029,%2D21%2C%2017%2D21.|title=French Open: Lakshya Sen loses to Heo Kwanghee in quarter-finals|work=ANI news|date=2021-10-29|accessdate=2022-06-17|archivedate=2022-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220617024421/https://www.aninews.in/news/sports/others/french-open-lakshya-sen-loses-to-heo-kwanghee-in-quarter-finals20211029191958/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。僅在[[德國|德國]]舉行的[[2021年海洛羽毛球公開賽|海洛公開賽]]闖進準決賽然而依舊不敵在荷蘭公開賽上擊敗他的駱建佑<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-kidambi-srikanth-lose-in-semifinals-of-hylo-open-101636248957665.html|title=Lakshya Sen, Kidambi Srikanth lose in semifinals of Hylo Open|work=Hindustan Times|date=2021-11-07|accessdate=2022-06-17|archivedate=2022-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402182806/https://www.hindustantimes.com/sports/badminton/lakshya-sen-kidambi-srikanth-lose-in-semifinals-of-hylo-open-101636248957665.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歐洲三站結束後，拉克什亞再轉戰在印尼舉辦的[[2021年印度尼西亞羽毛球大師賽|印尼大師賽]]、[[2021年印度尼西亞羽毛球公開賽|印尼公開賽]]和[[2021年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽總決賽|世界羽聯世界巡迴賽總決賽]]。在大師賽和公開賽上，他分別在次圈和首圈都不敵日本的[[桃田賢斗|桃田賢斗]]而淘汰<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportsdigest.in/indonesia-masters-2021-kento-momota-advances-into-the-quarter-finals-with-a-comfortable-victory-against-lakshya-sen/25053/|title=Indonesia Masters 2021: Kento Momota advances into the Quarter-finals with a comfortable victory against Lakshya Sen|work=Sports Digest|date=2021-11-18|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2021-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118065522/https://sportsdigest.in/indonesia-masters-2021-kento-momota-advances-into-the-quarter-finals-with-a-comfortable-victory-against-lakshya-sen/25053/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aninews.in/news/sports/others/indonesia-open-lakshya-sen-loses-to-world-number-one-kento-momota20211123171729/#:~:text=World%20number%20one%20Kento%20Momota%20defeated%20Lakshya%20Sen%2023%2D21,against%20Singapore's%20Loh%20Kean%20Yew.|title=Indonesia Open: Lakshya Sen loses to world number one Kento Momota|work=ANInews|date=2021-11-23|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618014410/https://www.aninews.in/news/sports/others/indonesia-open-lakshya-sen-loses-to-world-number-one-kento-momota20211123171729/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，拉克什亞在[[2021年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽|2021年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽]]年總排名第六得以獲得總決賽的參賽資格，他與[[安賽龍|安賽龍]]、[[桃田賢斗|桃田賢斗]]和[[拉斯穆斯·傑姆克|拉斯穆斯·傑姆克]]被分配至A組<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/504644497_121124660|title=看点满满！世界羽联总决赛抽签出炉，安赛龙桃田同在A组！ |work=搜狐体育|date=2021-12-01|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618020132/https://www.sohu.com/a/504644497_121124660|dead-url=no}}</ref>。桃田賢斗與傑姆克因傷痛問題而選擇退賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.badmintonplanet.com/badminton-news/18719-kento-momota-rasmus-gemke-withdraw-2021-bwf-world-tour-finals.html|title=Kento Momota and Rasmus Gemke Withdraw from 2021 BWF World Tour Finals|work=BadmintonPlanet,com|date=2021-12-02|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2021-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203152327/https://www.badmintonplanet.com/badminton-news/18719-kento-momota-rasmus-gemke-withdraw-2021-bwf-world-tour-finals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拉克什亞在小組賽面對安賽龍時以兩局不敵對手位居A組副盟晉級準決賽<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/sports/bwf-world-tour-finals-viktor-axelsen-deafeats-lakshya-sen-to-advance-to-next-stage-10181931.html|title=BWF World Tour Finals: Viktor Axelsen deafeats Lakshya Sen to advance to next stage|work=Firstpost|date=2021-12-02|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2021-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203160157/https://www.firstpost.com/sports/bwf-world-tour-finals-viktor-axelsen-deafeats-lakshya-sen-to-advance-to-next-stage-10181931.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。準決賽上，他再次對壘安賽龍但依然以0比2落敗<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32785941/bwf-world-tour-finals-2021-lakshya-sen-dream-run-ends-viktor-axelsen-lesson|title=BWF World Tour Finals: Lakshya Sen's dream run ends with Viktor Axelsen lesson|work=ESPN|date=2021-12-04|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2021-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211219172300/https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32785941/bwf-world-tour-finals-2021-lakshya-sen-dream-run-ends-viktor-axelsen-lesson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年12月，拉克什亞·森首次出戰在[[西班牙|西班牙]][[韋爾瓦|韋爾瓦]]舉行的[[2021年世界羽毛球錦標賽|世界錦標賽]]男子單打項目，他的首圈對手是[[德國|德國]]的[[麦克斯·魏斯基申|麦克斯·魏斯基申]]因對方退賽導致拉克什亞直接晉級次圈<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32865867/bwf-world-championships-2021-lakshya-sen-learns-art-rallies-enter-third-round|title=BWF World Championships: Lakshya Sen learns the art of rallies to enter third round|work=ESPN|date=2021-12-14|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606163727/https://www.espn.com/badminton/story/_/id/32865867/bwf-world-championships-2021-lakshya-sen-learns-art-rallies-enter-third-round|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他從次圈至半準決賽一路擊敗日本的[[西本拳太|西本拳太]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/bwf-world-championships-lakshya-sen-knocks-out-15th-seed-kenta-nishimoto-pv-sindhu-reaches-pre-quarterfinals-1887680-2021-12-14|title=BWF World Championships: Lakshya Sen knocks out 15th seed Kenta Nishimoto, PV Sindhu reaches pre-quarterfinals|work=India Today|date=2021-12-14|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215032401/https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/bwf-world-championships-lakshya-sen-knocks-out-15th-seed-kenta-nishimoto-pv-sindhu-reaches-pre-quarterfinals-1887680-2021-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]的[[凱文·科登|凱文·科登]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pandeglangnews.co.id/olahraga/pr-1632178805/kevin-cordon-kandas-di-bwf-world-championship-2021-tapi-sempat-curi-perhatian-dunia|title=Kevin Cordon Kandas di BWF World Championship 2021, Tapi Sempat Curi Perhatian Dunia|work=pandeglangnews|date=2021-12-17|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618024620/https://www.pandeglangnews.co.id/olahraga/pr-1632178805/kevin-cordon-kandas-di-bwf-world-championship-2021-tapi-sempat-curi-perhatian-dunia|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[中國|中國]]的[[趙俊鵬|趙俊鵬]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidesport.in/lakshya-sen-vs-zhao-jun-peng-live-indian-prodigy-eyes-potential-semi-final-clash-against-srikanth-follow-live-updates/|title=BWF World Championship: Lakshya Sen creates history, becomes youngest ever Indian male shuttler to enter semifinals of World Championships|work=Insidesport|date=2021-12-17|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618024808/https://www.insidesport.in/lakshya-sen-vs-zhao-jun-peng-live-indian-prodigy-eyes-potential-semi-final-clash-against-srikanth-follow-live-updates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>闖進準決賽。準決賽上，他以1比2（21比17、14比21、17比21）遭到師兄兼隊友[[斯里坎特·基達姆比|斯里坎特·基達姆比]]逆轉，首次出戰世錦賽便獲得季軍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/dehradun/lakshya-sen-clinches-bronze-at-world-badminton-championship/articleshow/88378494.cms|title=Lakshya Sen clinches bronze at World Badminton Championship|work=The Times of India|date=2021-12-20|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119134626/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/dehradun/lakshya-sen-clinches-bronze-at-world-badminton-championship/articleshow/88378494.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2022年1月，拉克什亞·森以三號種子的身份出戰[[2022年印度羽毛球公開賽|印度公開賽]]，他一路殺進決賽並對壘新科[[2021年世界羽毛球錦標賽|世界冠軍]]、新加坡的[[駱建佑|駱建佑]]，他以直落兩局挑落對手並成為第三位在印度公開賽奪得冠軍的東道主選手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pipanews.com/india-open-lakshya-sen-wins-first-india-open-singles-title-this-is-the-third-indian-to-win-this-award-lakshya-sen-won-the-india-open-badminton-tournament-beat-world-champion-loh-kean-yew/|title=India Open: Lakshya Sen wins first India Open singles title This is the third Indian to win this award Lakshya sen won the india open badminton tournament beat world champion loh kean yew|work=PiPa news|date=2022-01-17|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220618051338/https://pipanews.com/india-open-lakshya-sen-wins-first-india-open-singles-title-this-is-the-third-indian-to-win-this-award-lakshya-sen-won-the-india-open-badminton-tournament-beat-world-champion-loh-kean-yew/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年3月，拉克什亞再出戰[[2022年德國羽毛球公開賽|德國公開賽]]以及[[2022年全英羽毛球公開賽|全英公開賽]]，兩場賽事他都闖進了決賽。但他分別敗給了[[泰國|泰國]]的[[昆拉武特·威提讪|昆拉武特·威提讪]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/german-open-super-300-kunlavut-vitidsarn-outclasses-lakshya-sen-21-18-21-15-to-win-men-s-singles-title-1924935-2022-03-13|title=German Open Super 300: Kunlavut Vitidsarn outclasses Lakshya Sen 21-18, 21-15 to win men’s singles title|work=India Today|date=2022-03-13|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511031216/https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/badminton/story/german-open-super-300-kunlavut-vitidsarn-outclasses-lakshya-sen-21-18-21-15-to-win-men-s-singles-title-1924935-2022-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[丹麥|丹麥]]的[[安賽龍|安賽龍]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/en/news/all-england-open-badminton-championships-2022-lakshya-sen-vs-viktor-axelsen|title=All England Open Badminton Championships 2022: Lakshya Sen loses to Viktor Axelsen in final|work=Olympics|date=2022-03-21|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321045724/https://olympics.com/en/news/all-england-open-badminton-championships-2022-lakshya-sen-vs-viktor-axelsen|dead-url=no}}</ref>，連奪兩座亞軍，拉克什亞的[[世界羽聯世界排名|世界排名]]也在3月22日達到了前十名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/sports/lakshya-sen-breaks-into-top-10-of-bwf-badminton-world-rankings-news-188027|title=Lakshya Sen Breaks Into Top 10 Of BWF Badminton World Rankings|work=Outlook India|date=2022-03-22|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516175429/https://www.outlookindia.com/sports/lakshya-sen-breaks-into-top-10-of-bwf-badminton-world-rankings-news-188027|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，拉克什亞·森跟隨[[印度國家羽毛球隊|國家隊]]一同參加在[[泰國|泰國]][[曼谷|曼谷]]舉辦的男子團體比賽[[2022年湯姆斯盃|湯姆斯盃]]，拉克什亞共在此賽事中出場了五次並獲得了兩勝三負。他僅在小組賽首輪以及決賽戰勝了[[德國|德國]]的[[麦克斯·魏斯基申|麦克斯·魏斯基申]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/thomas-and-uber-cup-indian-mens-team-starts-campaign-with-resounding-5-0-win-over-germany-7906551/|title=Thomas and Uber Cup: Indian men’s team starts campaign with resounding 5-0 win over Germany|work=The Indian Express|date=2022-05-08|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523172531/https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/badminton/thomas-and-uber-cup-indian-mens-team-starts-campaign-with-resounding-5-0-win-over-germany-7906551/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[印尼|印尼]]的[[安东尼·金廷|安东尼·金廷]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-beats-anthony-ginting-thomas-cup-finals-2022-india-indonesia/article38492061.ece|title=Lakshya Sen after beating Ginting: 'I wasn't worried... this is for the team'|work=Sportstar|date=2022-05-15|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524065852/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/lakshya-sen-beats-anthony-ginting-thomas-cup-finals-2022-india-indonesia/article38492061.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在小組賽第三輪、八強賽以及四強賽分別敗給了[[中華台北|中華台北]]的[[周天成|周天成]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3923208|title=湯優盃》打3局沒在怕！周天成力退印度新一哥 台灣隊1：0領先|work=自由時報|date=2022-05-11|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511095915/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3923208|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]的[[李梓嘉|李梓嘉]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/sports/2022/05/12/486031|title=【汤杯】李梓嘉直落两局取胜印度　率先为大马拿下一分|work=東方日報|date=2022-05-12|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512151352/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/sports/2022/05/12/486031|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[丹麥|丹麥]]的[[安賽龍|安賽龍]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/thomas-cup-india-vs-denmark-semifinal-live-score-results-srikanth-lakshya-prannoy/article38490398.ece|title=India beats Denmark 3-2 to reach maiden Thomas Cup Final|work=Sportstar|date=2022-05-14|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220514232828/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/thomas-cup-india-vs-denmark-semifinal-live-score-results-srikanth-lakshya-prannoy/article38490398.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但最終印度還是以3比0橫掃了[[2020年湯姆斯盃|衛冕冠軍]]印尼，首度捧起湯姆斯盃<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/3177843/india-win-historic-first-thomas-cup-beating-indonesia-3-0|title=India win historic first Thomas Cup by beating Indonesia 3-0 in Thailand|work=South China Morning Post|date=2022-05-15|accessdate=2022-06-18|archivedate=2022-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609142122/https://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/3177843/india-win-historic-first-thomas-cup-beating-indonesia-3-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

